  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Porticus:  protecting migrants rights and abolishing modern-day slavery in Cambodia</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">DCA/CA and LSCW are seeking funds to implement a project &#x2018;Advocate for policies and legislative changes to protect migrants rights and to abolish modern day slavery&#x2019;. This will be achieved through building the capacity of returned migrants to voice their rights, raise awareness of safe migration, and hold the Cambodian government to account.</narrative>
